{"slideshow_credits": null, "snippet": "The Department of Veterans Affairs has taken steps to reduce delays faced by veterans, yet the waits are growing, not shrinking.", "abstract": "Editorial expresses alarm that number of veterans on wait lists to receive health care through Veterans Affairs Dept has risen by 50 percent since 2014, when scandal over long wait times was exposed; argues VA's efforts to increase access to care by hiring doctors and other personnel, expanding clinical space and authorizing outside care has failed to keep pace with soaring demand; calls for Congress to allocate resources needed to care for nation's veterans.", "section_name": "Opinion", "print_page": "20", "document_type": "article", "byline": {"person": [], "original": "By THE EDITORIAL BOARD", "organization": "THE EDITORIAL BOARD"}, "web_url": "http://www.nytimes.com/2015/07/08/opinion/ever-growing-waits-for-veterans-care.html", "lead_paragraph": "The Department of Veterans Affairs has taken steps to reduce delays faced by veterans, yet the waits are growing, not shrinking.", "headline": {"print_headline": "Ever-Growing Waits for Veterans\u2019 Care", "main": "Ever-Growing Waits for Veterans\u2019 Care", "content_kicker": "Editorial", "kicker": "Editorial"}, "_id": "559ccf3d38f0d81b1af2d593", "word_count": "472", "multimedia": [{"height": 126, "url": "images/2015/07/08/opinion/08wed3web/08wed3web-thumbWide.jpg", "legacy": {"wideheight": "126", "wide": "images/2015/07/08/opinion/08wed3web/08wed3web-thumbWide.jpg", "widewidth": "190"}, "subtype": "wide", "width": 190, "type": "image"}, {"height": 399, "url": "images/2015/07/08/opinion/08wed3web/08wed3web-articleLarge.jpg", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2015/07/08/opinion/08wed3web/08wed3web-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": "600", "xlargeheight": "399"}, "subtype": "xlarge", "width": 600, "type": "image"}, {"height": 75, "url": "images/2015/07/08/opinion/08wed3web/08wed3web-thumbStandard.jpg", "legacy": {"thumbnail": "images/2015/07/08